videos.description: Deatrick Nichols intercepts Logan Marchi in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Temple's fake FG goes horribly wrong

videos.description: Darius Tice sprints through the middle of the Owl defense for the score.
videos.headline: Tice takes it 47 yards untouched for the TD

videos.description: Tyre McCants completes the tip drill to give the Bulls a 4th and short in the 2nd quarter.
videos.headline: McCants tips the ball to himself to make catch

videos.description: Deatrick Nichols is having himself a night with 2 interceptions in the first half.
videos.headline: Nichols gets 2nd interception of the night

videos.description: Deatrick Nichols adds a forced fumble to his two interceptions in the first half.
videos.headline: Nichols continues dominance with forced  fumble

videos.headline: Temple's Martin takes the strip sack back for a TD

videos.description: Despite leading at the half, USF head coach Charlie Strong hopes his team will make fewer mistakes in the second half.
videos.headline: Strong reflects on his team's  performance in the 1st half

videos.headline: Abraham picks off  Nutile for USF's 4th takeaway

videos.headline: Tice scores his 2nd TD of the night
